type.description:
## Replacable

---


[Block Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/block_condition_types/replacable)

Checks whether the block is a replaceable material (e.g. tall grass, water, ...).

Type ID: `origins:replacable`

---

### Examples

```json
"block_condition": {
    "type": "origins:replacable"
}
```
